rows.confirm_comment:
1. The number of access users on the interface board is large: It is recommend to submit a ticket for capacity evaluation;
2. Invalid Packets attacks occur on the interface board: Eliminate external packet attacks according to description of ALM-21388 Invalid Packets Exceeding Alarm;
3. Interface board Forwarding surface resources is limited: It is recommended to implement the resource capacity assessment solution and refer to its output report processing;
4. Unknown reason: Please contact GTAC to analyze.

